---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import IntakeModal from '../components/intake.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="FAQs - Answers on Ideas to Loved Products Process" description="Common questions about our services: from product development and 3D printing to branding and public art. Learn how we turn your ideas into functional, adored realities.">

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Heading -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900">
        QUESTIONS BEFORE YOU START?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-4">
        Everything you need to know before turning your idea into a real product.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Container -->
    <div class="space-y-4">

      <!-- FAQ ITEM -->
      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-xl bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-500">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">
            I only have an idea in my head — is that enough?
          </h3>
          <span class="faq-icon text-xl transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
          Yes. That’s exactly where most of our clients start. You don’t need technical skills, drawings, or experience. We help you turn raw ideas into structured, buildable products step by step.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-xl bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-500">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">
            How fast can I actually get a working prototype?
          </h3>
          <span class="faq-icon text-xl transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
          Most projects move from idea to a working prototype within 14–21 days depending on complexity. Simple ideas can be even faster.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-xl bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-500">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">
            Do I need to know engineering, coding, or design?
          </h3>
          <span class="faq-icon text-xl transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
          Not at all. You focus on your idea — we handle design, engineering, prototyping, and technical execution.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-xl bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-500">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">
            What exactly will I receive at the end?
          </h3>
          <span class="faq-icon text-xl transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
          A functional prototype, 3D designs, product visuals, and a clear roadmap to launch — something real you can test, show, and present.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-xl bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-500">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">
            Can I use this to pitch investors or raise funding?
          </h3>
          <span class="faq-icon text-xl transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
          Yes. We help you move from “just an idea” to something investors can see, understand, and take seriously.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-xl bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-500">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">
            How does pricing actually work?
          </h3>
          <span class="faq-icon text-xl transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
          Pricing depends on complexity. We match your budget to the best possible outcome. No hidden fees.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-xl bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-500">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">
            Will my idea be safe with you?
          </h3>
          <span class="faq-icon text-xl transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
          Yes. We can work with NDAs and guide you on trademarks and patent strategies to protect your idea.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="text-center mt-12">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Still thinking about it?
    </p>

    <button id="/intake"
      class="bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg shadow-lg">
      GET YOUR IDEA BUILT TODAY →
    </button>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-3">
      No commitment. Just clarity on your idea.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
<script>
document.querySelectorAll(".faq-item").forEach(item => {
  item.addEventListener("mouseenter", () => {
    item.querySelector(".faq-icon").style.transform = "translateX(5px)";
  });

  item.addEventListener("mouseleave", () => {
    item.querySelector(".faq-icon").style.transform = "translateX(0)";
  });
});
</script>
</MainLayout>
